WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:02.566
Mom, that's not what you said

2
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:03.966
I'm not getting married.

3
00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:05.766
Don't blame me for being willful

4
00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:07.566
You married the Qin family as a slave girl

5
00:00:07.733 --> 00:00:10.066
That's the blessing you've cultivated in eight lifetimes

6
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:12.300
Sister, don't hesitate.

7
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.633
If you hesitate, the fool will be beaten to death

8
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:19.200
Kill you

9
00:00:20.733 --> 00:00:21.533
Let me eat.

10
00:00:22.266 --> 00:00:23.900
Haha, you get married obediently.

11
00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:25.800
As long as you serve Young Master Qin to me

12
00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:27.733
When I get 5 million dowry

13
00:00:27.733 --> 00:00:29.066
My first time

14
00:00:29.066 --> 00:00:31.266
Send that fool to the best Hu Yili

15
00:00:31.266 --> 00:00:34.466
Guaranteed to keep him safe for the rest of his life

16
00:00:34.766 --> 00:00:37.833
Otherwise they'll kill the fool

17
00:00:40.966 --> 00:00:42.900
Go home

18
00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:45.166
Go away Haoran

19
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.100
Nothing.

20
00:00:50.366 --> 00:00:53.000
Otherwise, I'm not sure.

21
00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.100
Sorry.

22
00:00:56.466 --> 00:01:00.000
I'm fine, wife, it doesn't hurt when you touch it.

23
00:01:01.766 --> 00:01:03.700
This is the only bride price you gave me in the first place

24
00:01:03.700 --> 00:01:05.400
I am not your wife today

25
00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:06.566
I'll give it back to you.

26
00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:09.800
From now on, you must protect yourself no matter where you are

27
00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:11.166
Remember?

28
00:01:18.866 --> 00:01:21.333
Wife, wife, where are you going?

29
00:01:21.333 --> 00:01:23.500
Wife, don't go

30
00:01:23.566 --> 00:01:28.366
Let go of my wife and come back

31
00:01:32.366 --> 00:01:36.300
Let go of me!

32
00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:40.600
5 million not enough flowers

